                        <ul>
                            <li><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><em>ALWAYS</em></span> keep the gun pointed in a safe directon.</li>
                            <li><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><em>ALWAYS</em></span> keep your finger <em>OFF</em> the trigger untill the gun is sighted on the target and you are ready to shoot.</li>
