                        <strong>
                            <li>Be sure your gun is safe to operate</li>
                            <li>Be familiar with your gun and know how to operate it safely</li>
                            <li>Use only the correct ammunition for your gun</li>
                            <li>Wear Eye and Ear protection as appropriate</li>
                            <li>Never use alcohol or drugs before or while shooting</li>
